### 健康检查
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/health

### 登录
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "Admin@123456"
}

### 使用说明
# 先执行“登录”接口，复制返回体中的 access_token，
# 再把下方所有 Authorization 里的 <ACCESS_TOKEN> 替换成真实值。

### 当前用户
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### 刷新令牌
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/auth/refresh
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### 首页看板
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### 分类列表
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/categories
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### 新增分类
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "category_name": "运维规范",
  "description": "运维制度与规范"
}

### 更新分类
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/categories/运维规范
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "category_name": "运维制度",
  "description": "运维制度与流程"
}

### 删除分类
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/categories/运维制度
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### 标签列表
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/tags
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### 新增标签
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/tags
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "tag_name": "手册",
  "description": "操作手册标签"
}

### 更新标签
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/tags/手册
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "tag_name": "说明书",
  "description": "说明书与手册标签"
}

### 删除标签
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/tags/说明书
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### 用户列表
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/users
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### 角色列表
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/roles
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### 新增用户
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "username": "viewer",
  "role_name": "普通用户",
  "department": "财务",
  "email": "viewer@example.com",
  "password": "Viewer@123456"
}

### 更新用户
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/users/3
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "username": "viewer",
  "role_name": "知识管理员",
  "department": "知识运营",
  "email": "viewer-updated@example.com",
  "password": "Viewer@654321"
}

### 重置用户密码
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/users/3/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "password": "Viewer@654321"
}

### 删除用户
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/users/3
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### 收藏列表
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/favorites
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### 最近阅读
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/read-records/recent
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### 文档列表
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/documents
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### 文档详情
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/documents/1
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### 文档分段
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/documents/1/segments
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### 文档 FAQ
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/documents/1/faqs
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### 新增 FAQ
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/documents/1/faqs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "question": "权限开通后如何确认？",
  "answer": "由申请人登录后自行验证。"
}

### 更新 FAQ
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/faqs/2
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "question": "权限开通后如何验证？",
  "answer": "由申请人登录数据库后自行验证。"
}

### 删除 FAQ
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/faqs/2
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### 记录阅读
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/documents/1/read
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### 切换收藏
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/documents/1/favorite
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### 新增文档
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/documents
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "title": "报销制度说明",
  "summary": "用于演示新增文档接口。",
  "content": "1. 发票需在7日内提交。\n2. 部门负责人审批后进入财务复核。",
  "category_name": "财务制度",
  "tags": ["报销", "财务"],
  "change_note": "初始化文档"
}

### 发布文档
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/documents/1/publish
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### 重建文档分段
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/documents/1/reindex
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### 更新文档并生成新版本
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/documents/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "title": "数据库权限申请流程（修订）",
  "summary": "补充了审批与开通说明。",
  "content": "1. 提交权限申请单。\n2. 直属主管审批。\n3. DBA 审核后开通只读账号。\n4. 开通后由申请人确认。",
  "category_name": "制度流程",
  "tags": ["数据库", "权限", "流程", "修订"],
  "change_note": "补充开通确认步骤"
}

### 归档文档
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/documents/1/archive
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### 智能问答
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/qa/ask
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

{
  "question_text": "如何申请数据库权限？"
}

### Agent 记录
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/agent-runs
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### 问答历史
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/questions/history
Authorization: Bearer <ACCESS_TOKEN>

### Qdrant 创建 demo collection（可选）
PUT http://127.0.0.1:6333/collections/zhishu_segments_demo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vectors": {
    "size": 8,
    "distance": "Cosine"
  }
}

### Qdrant upsert demo points（可选）
# 先执行 infra/scripts/export-qdrant-demo-points.ps1 生成 artifacts/qdrant-demo-points.json，
# 再将 points 数组复制到下方请求体中，或直接执行 infra/scripts/sync-qdrant-demo.ps1。
PUT http://127.0.0.1:6333/collections/zhishu_segments_demo/points?wait=true
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "points": []
}

### Qdrant demo 查询（可选）
POST http://127.0.0.1:6333/collections/zhishu_segments_demo/points/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": [0.2, 0.1, 0.9, 0.7, 0.3, 0.4, 0.2, 0.6],
  "limit": 3,
  "with_payload": true,
  "with_vector": false
}
